rvice \\u2013 Academic Course and start growing your knowledgebase! All about Hospitality.\"]', '799', 1, 399, 'intermediate', 1, NULL, '', 1619395200, 1619395200, 'general', 30, 1, 1, 'active', '', 'hospitality,food and beverage,online course,course,keynote course,food and beverage service online course,F&B Service Course,food knowledge,beverage knowledge,connaisseur,hospitality connaisseur,Attributes of Waiter,Classification of Beverages,Process of Making Coffee,Food & Beverage Equipment,F&B Departmental Hierarchy,Type of Meals,Process of Restaurant Reservation,Meaning of Sideboard,Process of Making Tea,Job Description of Waiter,hotel,restaurant,hotel management,restaurant management,steward learning,restaurant learnings,hotel management free courses,hospitality free courses', 'Food & Beverage Service Academic Course by Hospitality Connaisseur is an Intermediate Course to learn about the Food & Beverage Service Department of a Hotel.', 1);
