as now come to the forefront. The importance of Human Resources to any organization need not be overemphasized.\",\"Human Resource is the wealth of a Nation and an Organization. The development process is Wide and Varied as the Basics of \\u2018Human Resource Management\\u2019 are discussed in this Lesson. Don\\u2019t Wait SUBSCRIBE NOW and start learning HR Skills.\"]', '0', NULL, 0, 'intermediate', 1, NULL, '', 1619395200, 1619395200, 'general', 30, 0, 1, 'active', '', 'hospitality,connaisseur,hospitality connaisseur,hospitality connaisseur courses,hotel management courses,human resource management,HRM Course,HRM,HR Course,HRM free course,hotel management free course,HM free courses,Basics of Human Resources,Definition of HRM,Organizational Significance of HRM,Social Significance of HRM,Professional Significance of HRM,Intellectual Capital Management,Social Capital Management,Emotional Capital Management,Personal Aspect of HRM,Welfare Aspect of HRM,Industrial Aspect of HRM,Different Objectives of HRM,Innumerable,Trustworthy,Retention,Pervasive,Auxiliary,Retrenchment,Parlance,Human Capital,Cognitive,Collaborative', 'After attending this course, you will be able to Define Human Resource Management, Understand the Nature and Scope of Human Resource Management, Describe the development of Human Resource Management in India, and Detail the objectives of Human Resource Management.', 1);
