cific query, please write us on </span>\r\n                                                                                                                                            <a class=\"text-theme\" href=\"mailto:support@hospitalityconnaisseur.com\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">support@hospitalityconnaisseur.com</span></a>\r\n                                                                                                                                        </p>\r\n                                                                                                                                        <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b xss=\"removed\"><br></b></span></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                        <h3 xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">18. SEVERABILITY</span></h3>\r\n                                                                                                                                        <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b xss=\"removed\"><br></b></span></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                        <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">If any provision of this Policy is held by a court of competent jurisdiction to be contrary to law, such provision shall be changed and interpreted so as to best accomplish the objectives of the original provision to the fullest extent allowed by the law and the remaining provisions of this Policy will remain in full force and effect.</span></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                        <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b xss=\"removed\"><br></b></span></p>\r\n                                                                    