                                                     <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Service Functionality, The Website from time-to-time, is subject to Connaisseur Futuretech Private Limited (INDIA). Hospitality Connaisseur – Accelerating Hospitality, Empowering Hoteliers. India’s 1st Hospitality centric Media and Technology Company, believes to connect each hospitality individual to the vast & various amount of knowledge by providing Boost, Backup and Motivation for their professional growth journey via Online Courses, Magazines, Podcasts, News and Daily relevant Articles on The Hospitality Industry.</span></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Those who choose to access the Website from other locations do so at their own initiative and are responsible for compliance with local laws. Any offer for any product, service, and/or information made in connection with the Services is void where prohibited, If. For any specific query, please write us on </span>\r\n                                                                                                                                                        <span xss=\"removed\"><a class=\"text-theme\" href=\"mailto:support@hospitalityconnaisseur.com\">support@hospitalityconnaisseur.com</a></span>\r\n                                                                                                                                                            </span>    </p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <p xss=\"removed\"><br></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <h3 xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">21. FUTURE BUSINESS TRANSACTIONS</span></h3>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <p></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <p xss=\"removed\"><b xss=\"removed\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-fb539c6c-7fff-8027-57bd-3879afcb2249\"><br></b></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">As we continue to develop our business, we might undergo a change of ownership such as a merger and/or a sale of all or substantially all our stock or assets or We might buy potential companies to enhance our offerings, In such cases, user information generally is one of the transferred business assets, and by submitting any data or contributions (collectively, “Data”) to us, you agree that such Data may be transferred to such parties in these circumstances or will be received through Acquisitions. However, any party purchasing our assets will be subject to an obligation to maintain the integrity of your personally identifiable information as we will do the same if we acquire relevant companies in the future.</span></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                    <p xss=\"removed\"><b xss=\"removed\"><br></b></p>\r\n                                                                                                                                                        <h3 xss=